            "text": " to adopting a national health insurance program last week, when Democratic lawmakers reintroduced a Medicare for All bill in the U.S. House of Representatives, and the Senate confirmed Xavier Becerra, a past advocate for such a system, to serve as Health and Human Services Secretary.",
